column5: Yesterday as we were driving back from the reserve i decided to stop by the grand for a few casts. The water was nice and calm fish jumping everywhere, as we were ready to go i got a hit on my lure much to my surprise it was a gar pike...first one ever for me....i guess there spawing now cuz they were biting like crazy..anyways here's a pic of a first for me!    C:\Users\Valued Customer\Pictures\2008-06-03 nowe\nowe 057.JPG
